Aristarchus Grammar:

program = def ... question ...


def = (body Identifier Number Number)
    | (connection Identifier Identifier Identifier Number)
    | (define-system Identifier Variable ...)



question = variable 
         | (lagrange variable variable)
         | (L1 variable variable)
         | (L2 variable variable)
         | (L3 variable variable)
         | (L4 variable variable)
         | (L5 variable variable)
         | (kepler3-period variable variable)
         | (escape-velocity variable)
         | (surface-gravity variable)

